===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|tangentem}}, the accusative of {{m|la|tangēns||touching}} (in the phrase {{term||[[linea#Latin|līnea]] [[tango#Latin|tangēns]]|a touching line}}), the [[present participle]] of the verb {{m|la|tangō||touch|pos=verb}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*tag-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*taǵ-||to touch}}. Cognate with {{cog|ang|þaccian||to touch lightly, pat, stroke}}. More at {{l|en|thack}}, {{l|en|thwack}}.

